Subject: Secunia Research: VMWare VMnc Codec Mismatched
	Dimensions Buffer Overflow

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 07/09/2009

      - VMWare VMnc Codec Mismatched Dimensions Buffer Overflow -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

